{"prompt": "Build a portfolio for a UI/UX designer. The overall look should be user-friendly, incorporating a mustard yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Sarah Chen - UI/UX Designer</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #e8b84d; /* Mustard Yellow */\n            --secondary-color: #f0d599;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --footer-background: #f8f8f8;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        #about {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        #about h2,\n        #portfolio h2,\n        #contact h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n\n        #about p {\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .project-card {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .project-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .project-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .project-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .project-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .project-info p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .project-info a {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 10px 15px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .project-info a:hover {\n            background-color: #d4a03e;\n        }\n\n        #contact form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        #contact label {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact input,\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding and border in the element's total width and height */\n        }\n\n        #contact textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        #contact button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: #d4a03e;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-background);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Sarah Chen</h1>\n            <p>UI/UX Designer | Crafting intuitive and delightful digital experiences.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Me</h2>\n            <p>\n                I am a passionate UI/UX designer with a knack for translating complex ideas into simple, elegant, and user-centric designs. My approach focuses on understanding user needs, conducting thorough research, and iterating through prototypes to create seamless and engaging digital products.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"portfolio\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>My Work</h2>\n            <div class=\"portfolio-grid\">\n                <div class=\"project-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/e8b84d/ffffff?text=Project+1+Thumbnail\" alt=\"Project 1 Thumbnail\">\n                    <div class=\"project-info\">\n                        <h3>E-commerce App Redesign</h3>\n                        <p>Revamped the user interface and experience for a popular online retail app, focusing on improved navigation and checkout flow.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#project1\">View Case Study</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"project-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/e8b84d/ffffff?text=Project+2+Thumbnail\" alt=\"Project 2 Thumbnail\">\n                    <div class=\"project-info\">\n                        <h3>SaaS Dashboard Design</h3>\n                        <p>Designed a clean and functional dashboard for a new Software as a Service platform, prioritizing data visualization and user efficiency.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#project2\">View Case Study</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"project-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/e8b84d/ffffff?text=Project+3+Thumbnail\" alt=\"Project 3 Thumbnail\">\n                    <div class=\"project-info\">\n                        <h3>Mobile Game Interface</h3>\n                        <p>Created an engaging and intuitive interface for a casual mobile game, enhancing player immersion and usability.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#project3\">View Case Study</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Sarah Chen. All rights reserved. | Built with &hearts; | <a href=\"mailto:sarah.chen.ux@email.com\">sarah.chen.ux@email.com</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! I will get back to you soon.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}